    "description": "MUSCAT GROUP Inc. provides marketing support services using SNS data analysis tools in Japan. It company develops and operates community data management tool CCXcloud, a platform for managing and analysis of community data from market research. The company also provides marketing solutions using community data; beauty products under the MiiS brand, fashion products under the RiLi Store name, energy drink under the HICAT Hi-Energy brand name, clothing products under the RANCLIC brand name, and sleep interior products under the SUYALI brand name. In addition, it offers MiiLabo, a review-based real life beauty information media community; Honeycomb-KOREA, a Korean information media community; mochimochi Jpn, a Japanese culture information community for Korean girls; Simple Home, a housing and living media community; RiLi.tokyo, a media community that provides information on fashion, beauty, spots, etc.; RINNEKO, a virtual paradise; and CCProduction, a production company. The company was formerly known as Ricecurry Inc. and changed its name to MUSCAT GROUP Inc. in July 2025. MUSCAT GROUP Inc. was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Shibuya, Japan."
